  "description": "Based on the short story \"Ghost Toilet\" from Toru Tsunemitsu's urban myth collection \"School Ghost Stories.\" This was adapted into the children's book \"Hanako in the Toilet: Scary Stories of Your School\" (1993). Several artists then adapted this into the \"Here Comes Hanako\" manga; most of them also wrote the anime version, which was aired as a segment of the TV series \"Ponkikki Kids.\" Episodes, introduced by Hanako, included \"The Haunted Cinema\" and \"The Cursed Promise Ring.\" ",
